From 394679f322649d06fea3c646ba65f5a0887f52c3 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Jinjie Ruan <ruanjinjie@huawei.com>
Date: Thu, 12 Sep 2024 16:30:20 +0800
Subject: [PATCH] drm/msm/adreno: Use IRQF_NO_AUTOEN flag in request_irq()
Git-commit: 394679f322649d06fea3c646ba65f5a0887f52c3
Patch-mainline: v6.13-rc1
References: git-fixes

disable_irq() after request_irq() still has a time gap in which
interrupts can come. request_irq() with IRQF_NO_AUTOEN flag will
disable IRQ auto-enable when request IRQ.

Fixes: 4b565ca5a2cb ("drm/msm: Add A6XX device support")
Reviewed-by: Dmitry Baryshkov <dmitry.baryshkov@linaro.org>
Signed-off-by: Jinjie Ruan <ruanjinjie@huawei.com>
Patchwork: https://patchwork.freedesktop.org/patch/614075/
Signed-off-by: Rob Clark <robdclark@chromium.org>
Acked-by: Takashi Iwai <tiwai@suse.de>

---
 drivers/gpu/drm/msm/adreno/a6xx_gmu.c | 4 +---
 1 file changed, 1 insertion(+), 3 deletions(-)

diff --git a/drivers/gpu/drm/msm/adreno/a6xx_gmu.c b/drivers/gpu/drm/msm/adreno/a6xx_gmu.c
index 37927bdd6fbe..14db7376c712 100644
--- a/drivers/gpu/drm/msm/adreno/a6xx_gmu.c
+++ b/drivers/gpu/drm/msm/adreno/a6xx_gmu.c
@@ -1522,15 +1522,13 @@ static int a6xx_gmu_get_irq(struct a6xx_gmu *gmu, struct platform_device *pdev,
 
 	irq = platform_get_irq_byname(pdev, name);
 
-	ret = request_irq(irq, handler, IRQF_TRIGGER_HIGH, name, gmu);
+	ret = request_irq(irq, handler, IRQF_TRIGGER_HIGH | IRQF_NO_AUTOEN, name, gmu);
 	if (ret) {
 		DRM_DEV_ERROR(&pdev->dev, "Unable to get interrupt %s %d\n",
 			      name, ret);
 		return ret;
 	}
 
-	disable_irq(irq);
-
 	return irq;
 }
 
